ing=1><TR><TD valign=top><B><FONT FACE="Verdana,Arial" SIZE=1 COLOR=#000000>Author</FONT><B></TD><TD valign=top><B><FONT FACE="Verdana,Arial" SIZE=1 COLOR=#000000>Comment</FONT><B></FONT></TD></TR><TR BGCOLOR=#6B8E23><TD NOWRAP width=20% valign=top align=left><B><FONT FACE="Verdana,Arial" SIZE=2><A HREF=http://pub10.ezboard.com/ugharadin.showPublicProfile?language=EN>Gharadin</A>&nbsp; <IMG SRC=http://www.ezboard.com/ezgfx/gicons/black_ball.gif BORDER=0 WIDTH=10 HEIGHT=10></FONT></B><BR><FONT FACE="Verdana,Arial" SIZE=1>Registered User</FONT><BR><FONT FACE="Verdana,Arial" SIZE=1>(</FONT><FONT FACE="Verdana,Arial" SIZE=1 COLOR=#5F9EA0>4/18/01</FONT> <FONT FACE="Verdana,Arial" SIZE=1 COLOR=#5F9EA0>12:08:53 am</FONT><FONT FACE="Verdana,Arial" SIZE=1>)<BR></FONT><A HREF=http://pub10.ezboard.com/fforgottentruthforeignlegiongeneral.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=559.topic><FONT FACE="Verdana,Arial" SIZE=1>Reply</FONT></A></TD><TD VALIGN=TOP ALIGN=LEFT><B><FONT SIZE=2 FACE="Verdana,Arial">New Lugian town is open for business</font></B><HR><FONT SIZE=2 FACE="Verdana,Arial">Dia and myself visited the new Lugian town of Linvak Tukal tonight, very cool-looking place! It's a huge weird castle up in the mountains east of Qalaba'r, around 77.2S, 28.5E. It looks really impressive from down below. To actually get into the castle, you have to go through a huge citadel-looking dungeon. The dungeon entrance portal is down in a valley near 76.7S, 28.0E. The dungeon is kind of confusing, but basically try to keep going up ramps, and if you come to a room with some big rocks in it, the portal into the castle is just through there. It might be pretty dangerous in there during off-hours, but I'm not even sure what kind of Lugians are in there, they were all dead by the time we got to them (the place was packed).<br>
<br>
The castle is very cool looking, all towers and ramps and little rooms built into the walls. The lugians in town were friendly enough, although the chief's pet mattekar kept growling at me. He liked Dia though, must be that french perfume! There's a new crafter guy in their armory, who's looking for trophies from high-level lugians. Not sure what kind of trophies, or what he gives you in return. Another lugian gave us an odd book and said something about totems, but I have no idea what that is all about.<br>
<br>
All the lugians got a makeover with this patch, I think they're the best looking critters in the game now. If there was nothing else in this patch except for the castle and the new lugian look, I'd still say it was a great patch!</font><P><P><i></i></TD></TR><TR BGCOLOR=#2f2f4f><TD NOWRAP width=20% valign=top align=left><B><FONT FACE="Verdana,Arial" SIZE=2><A HREF=http://pub10.ezboard.com/bforgottentruthforeignlegion.showLocalUserPublicProfile?login=dia>Dia</A>&nbsp; <IMG SRC=http://www.ezboard.com/ezgfx/gicons/black_thatch.gif BORDER=0 WIDTH=10 HEIGHT=10></FONT></B><BR><FONT FACE="Verdana,Arial" SIZE=1>Registered User</FONT><BR><FONT FACE="Verdana,Arial" SIZE=1>(</FONT><FONT FACE="Verdana,Arial" SIZE=1 COLOR=#5F9EA0>4/19/01</FONT> <FONT FACE="Verdana,Arial" SIZE=1 COLOR=#5F9EA0>9:09:20 am</FONT><FONT FACE="Verdana,Arial" SIZE=1>)<BR></FONT><A HREF=http://pub10.ezboard.com/fforgottentruthforeignlegiongeneral.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=559.topic&index=1><FONT FACE="Verdana,Arial" SIZE=1>Reply</FONT></A></TD><TD VALIGN=TOP ALIGN=LEFT><B><FONT SIZE=2 FACE="Verdana,Arial">luggians</font></B><HR><FONT SIZE=2 FACE="Verdana,Arial">I've seen all kind of luggians in there. Some with hollow weapons and some with regular weapons. Regular luggians and Raiders up to extas. People were talking of a Taitus Raider but, I didn't see it myself. I camped the final room for about 30 min along with bunch of other players but didn't see anything else than extas. People were waiting for a commander and something else, but it never showed up while I was there. I saw a player with a luggian armor, very nice looking, al 160 he said.</font><P><P><i></i></TD></TR></TABLE><TABLE BORDER=0 WIDTH=95%><TR><TD ALIGN=LEFT></TD><TD ALIGN=RIGHT><A HREF=http://pub10.ezboard.com/fforgottentruthforeignlegiongeneral.showMessage?topicID=557.topic><FONT FACE="Verdana,Arial" SIZE=1><< Prev Topic</FONT></A> &nbsp;<A HREF=http://pub10.ezboard.com/fforgottentruthforeignlegiongeneral.showMessage?topicID=